item.title: CVE-2020-7852|2024-09-17T01:36:01.501Z -- humantalk -- daviewindy
item.description: DaviewIndy has a Heap-based overflow vulnerability, triggered when the user opens a malformed ex.j2c format file that is mishandled by Daview.exe. Attackers could exploit this and arbitrary code execution.
